            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>The couvade has always seemed to me the most extraordinary of all the odd customs followed by man. Your idea is new to me, and very ingenious; but I do not think that it can be admitted, as the period when male mammals suckled their young must have been so immensely remote, seeing that rudimentary mammæ are common to all orders, including the marsupials.</p>
                    </div>
